items.name: Origami.chat
items.tagline: Find your perfect leads with one prompt
items.description: Provide a prompt and get your perfect leads. origami.chat has 100+ data sources - use it to find more of your perfect customers, enrich a CSV, or get decision makers. Try it out and get a lead list in seconds!

items.name: Clawi.ai
items.tagline: OpenClaw in the Cloud with Zero Setup and on 24/7
items.description: Stop wrestling with servers. Get your private OpenClaw assistant running in 5 minutes. Works on WhatsApp, Telegram, and Discord while you sleep.

items.name: Reloop
items.tagline: Create winning ads without prompts or skills
items.description: Unlike other AI tools that need you to be a prompting pro, Reloop uses a conversational creative agent. Just chat about your idea, the agent gets your product, suggests a creative plan, and boom, full video generated. No prompts to tweak, no technical settings to mess with. Reloop brings together custom avatars, cloned voices, built-in video editor and auto captions all in one spot. From idea to ad ready to scale in minutes, not days

items.name: Monologue for iOS
items.tagline: Turn your voice into polished writing‚Äîwherever you go.
items.description: Monologue turns your voice into polished writing‚Äîinside the apps you already use. From coding in the terminal to sending a quick message to grandpa, Monologue is the shortest distance between speech and writing. Unlike basic dictation, Monologue doesn't just transcribe. It rewrites, removes filler words, adds punctuation, and adapts to context. Your texts sound like texts. Your emails sound human. Your notes turn into clean lists and structured thoughts.

items.name: FF Designer
items.tagline: Generate beautiful UI designs that you can instantly edit
items.description: AI design tools promise speed but deliver slow outputs, endless re-prompting, and lost momentum. FF Designer generates polished screens in seconds and lets you edit everything visually. No loops, just flow. Download or export, your choice

items.name: Kollect Voice Agent
items.tagline: No Boring Forms. Just Voice Conversations
items.description: Kollect turns boring forms into real-time AI conversations. Users speak naturally, AI listens and dynamically guides the survey. You can even create forms by simply describing them.

items.name: HyperCaps for macOS
items.tagline: Turn CapsLock into a Super Key & Boost Productivity
items.description: Stop "finger gymnastics" with complex shortcuts! HyperCaps turns your wasted CapsLock key into a macOS productivity superpower. ü™Ñ Core Features: ‚ú® Hyper Key: Hold CapsLock to trigger Cmd+Opt+Ctrl+Shift. üöÄ Vim Mode: Navigate using H/J/K/L without leaving the home row. üß† Smart Tap: Tap for Escape or CapsLock. Native, lightweight (SwiftUI), and privacy-first (zero logging). üéÅ PH Community: Use code PHLAUNCH20 for 20% off lifetime access!

items.name: Decks For Good
items.tagline: Get fundraising advice when you give to charity
items.description: Want to crush your fundraise? Get feedback from investors who've written hundreds of checks and repeat founders with multiple exits. With Decks For Good, you can donate to a vetted nonprofit and get detailed feedback on your fundraising pitch. You might even score an investment! 100% of your donation goes to charity - we don't process payments, all donations are made directly to the nonprofit.

items.name: AgentReady
items.tagline: Cut your AI token costs by 40-60% with one API call
items.description: AgentReady is an API toolkit that makes the web readable for AI agents. Our flagship tool TokenCut compresses text before it hits GPT-4, Claude, or any LLM ‚Äî same meaning, fewer tokens, lower bill. Plus 6 more tools: MD Converter, Sitemap Generator, LLMO Auditor, Structured Data, Robots.txt Analyzer, and Image Proxy. Free during beta. 3 lines of code to integrate.

items.name: Mengram
items.tagline: AI memory API with 3 types: facts, events, and workflows
items.description: AI memory API with 3 types: semantic (facts), episodic (events), and procedural (learned workflows). One API call extracts all three automatically. Killer feature: your agent completes a task ‚Üí Mengram saves the steps ‚Üí next time it already knows the optimal path with success/failure tracking. Works with Claude (MCP), LangChain, CrewAI, OpenClaw. Free, open-source, Apache 2.0.
